---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Agent as Declarative agent
    participant Store as Token store
    participant Plugin as Plugin<br/>(MCP server or REST API)

    User->>Agent: "How much is left in the Fourth Coffee lobby renovation budget?"

    rect rgb(238, 243, 251)
        opt MCP plugin with dynamic tool discovery
            Agent->>Plugin: Request current tools (tools/list)
            Plugin-->>Agent: Return tool definitions
            Agent->>Agent: Validate new or changed tools
        end
    end

    Note over Agent: Match prompt to GetBudget tool<br/>(budgetName = "Fourth Coffee lobby renovation")

    rect rgb(255, 244, 224)
        Note over User, Agent: Consent
        Agent->>User: Ask to allow sending data to the plugin
        User-->>Agent: Allow once or always allow
    end

    rect rgb(253, 235, 236)
        opt Plugin requires authentication
            Agent->>Store: Request token or API key
            Store-->>Agent: Return token or key<br/>(prompt sign-in if needed)
        end
    end

    rect rgb(230, 244, 234)
        Note over Agent, Plugin: Request and response
        Agent->>Plugin: Send request with parameters
        Plugin-->>Agent: Return response<br/>{ "availableFunds": 5000.00 }
        Agent->>User: "The available funds left in the Fourth Coffee lobby renovation budget are $5,000."
    end
